platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 利用球術破關，踢出驚喜世界波
サッカー史に残る名場面を再現
提腳射門 創造足壇傳奇

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Always wanted to be a soccer star? Score! Hero puts you in the kit of a young upstart, making your way to bigger and better clubs. The controls couldn’t be simpler—simply draw a line where you want the ball to go, and let the action unfold. While the gameplay is easy to learn, Score! Hero also shines with depth, rewarding thoughtful passes and smart shots over wild swiping.
